OL,3,CPrisoner's brother warns 'torturous'
OL,4,CIPP sentences will cause deaths in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FRoddy Russell is warning that his
OL,8,Fbrother, who is serving an indefinite
OL,9,Fsentence, could die in prison - ITV
OL,10,FWest Country's Political Correspondent
OL,11,FLucy McDaid reports
OL,13,FA man from the Forest of Dean whose
OL,14,Fbrother is serving an indefinite jail
OL,15,Fterm has warned the government that
OL,16,Fthere will be deaths in custody if
OL,17,Fprisoners serving the now-banned
OL,18,Fsentence aren't dealt with quickly.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
