OL,3,CPrisoner's brother warns 'torturous'
OL,4,CIPP sentences will cause deaths in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FRob Russell is one of 1,095 prisoners
OL,8,Fstill serving an imprisonment for
OL,9,Fpublic protection (IPP) sentence who
OL,10,Fhave never been released from prison,
OL,11,Fdespite IPPs being banned in 2012.
OL,13,F"It's an absolute nightmare, it never
OL,14,Fgoes from me, it's in my head every
OL,15,Fday," Rob's brother, Roddy, told ITV
OL,16,FWest Country. "There isn't a day that
OL,17,Fgoes by where I don't try to do
OL,18,Fsomething to persuade the powers that
OL,19,Fbe that this IPP sentence needs to be
OL,20,Fresolved."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
