OL,3,CPrisoner's brother warns 'torturous'
OL,4,CIPP sentences will cause deaths in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FRob was handed an IPP sentence in 2009
OL,8,Fafter pleading guilty to making a
OL,9,Fthreat to kill, with a minimum tariff
OL,10,Fof two and a half years. He worked as
OL,11,Fa welder in Gloucestershire before
OL,12,Fdeveloping problems with his mental
OL,13,Fhealth and an addiction to alcohol.
OL,15,F"The nearest that I'd come to the
OL,16,Fcriminal justice system was a speeding
OL,17,Ffine and Rob was the same," says Roddy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
