OL,7,F"Up until this point I thought, you do
OL,8,Fyour crime, spend your time in prison,
OL,9,Fand come out at your two and a half
OL,10,Fyear point."
OL,12,FBut Rob's sentence was an IPP.
OL,14,FWhat are Imprisonment for Public
OL,15,FProtection (IPP) sentences?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
