OL,3,CPrisoner's brother warns 'torturous'
OL,4,CIPP sentences will cause deaths in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FThey were introduced by Labour under
OL,8,Fthe Criminal Justice Act 2003, and
OL,9,Ffirst imposed in 2005. They were
OL,10,Fintended for offenders convicted of
OL,11,Fone or more serious violent or sexual
OL,12,Foffences which didn't warrant a life
OL,13,Fsentence, but where the offender was
OL,14,Fconsidered a serious danger to the
OL,15,Fpublic in future.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
