OL,3,CPrisoner's brother warns 'torturous'
OL,4,CIPP sentences will cause deaths in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FOnce the minimum tariff had been
OL,8,Fserved, it was then up to the Parole
OL,9,FBoard to decide if the offender was
OL,10,Fdeemed safe enough for public life. If
OL,11,Freleased, they would be on licence and
OL,12,Frecalled to prison if in breach of
OL,13,Ftheir conditions or guilty of other
OL,14,Foffences.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
