OL,3,CPrisoner's brother warns 'torturous'
OL,4,CIPP sentences will cause deaths in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FUp until very recently, an offender
OL,8,Fwould need to wait 10 years on licence
OL,9,Fbefore they were able to apply to have
OL,10,Ftheir licence terminated. Under
OL,11,Fchanges implemented by the previous
OL,12,FTory government - as part of the
OL,13,FVictims and Prisoners Act 2024 - IPP
OL,14,Foffenders released from custody at
OL,15,Fleast five years ago, but not sent
OL,16,Fback to prison in the past two years,
OL,17,Fwill have their licences automatically
OL,18,Fterminated.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
