OL,3,CPrisoner's brother warns 'torturous'
OL,4,CIPP sentences will cause deaths in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FEligibility for the Parole Board to
OL,8,Fterminate licences has also been
OL,9,Fdropped from 10 years, to three.
OL,11,FThere is a huge amount of positivity
OL,12,Fwithin government about the changes,
OL,13,Fbut the families of the prisoners who
OL,14,Fhave never been released want all IPP
OL,15,Fprisoners given some kind of
OL,16,Fresolution.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
