OL,3,CPrisoner's brother warns 'torturous'
OL,4,CIPP sentences will cause deaths in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FRoddy says: "They've all developed a
OL,8,Fmental health impairment as a direct
OL,9,Fresult of the IPP sentence. They
OL,10,F(government) are trying to claim they
OL,11,Fcan treat them in prison, but if
OL,12,Fprison is the place making them
OL,13,Funwell, then prison isn't the right
OL,14,Fplace to treat them."
OL,16,F"They (IPP prisoners) are now victims
OL,17,Fof torture from the government in my
OL,18,Fopinion," he adds.
