OL,3,CPrisoner's brother warns 'torturous'
OL,4,CIPP sentences will cause deaths in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FThe sentences are widely acknowledged
OL,8,Fas being a 'stain' on the UK's justice
OL,9,Fsystem, not just by campaigners but
OL,10,Fmany politicians too.
OL,12,FLord David Blunkett, the Labour former
OL,13,FHome Secretary who helped introduce
OL,14,Fthem, has previously admitted that
OL,15,Ftheir introduction is one of his
OL,16,Fbiggest regrets in government.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
