OL,4,CIPP sentences will cause deaths in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FTalking about his brother, Rob says
OL,8,Fhe's now too mentally unwell to prove
OL,9,Fhe can be released, describing his
OL,10,Fsituation as an "awful vicious cycle",
OL,11,Fsimilar to that of others in the
OL,12,Fremaining "cohort" of IPP prisoners.
OL,14,FThe Ministry of Justice says: "It is
OL,15,Fright that IPP sentences were
OL,16,Fabolished. With public protection as
OL,17,Fthe number one priority, the Lord
OL,18,FChancellor has just announced plans to
OL,19,Fsignificantly shorten the license
OL,20,Fperiods for rehabilitated offenders on
OL,21,Fthese sentences.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
